
# SIEM Notes

## What is SIEM?

Security Information and Event Management is a security solution used to:

* Collect logs
* Monitor systems
* Detect threats
* Generate alerts
* Support incident response

---

# SIEM Workflow

```text
Devices/Servers
      ↓
Log Collection
      ↓
SIEM Analysis
      ↓
Correlation Rules
      ↓
Alerts & Dashboards
```

---

# Main Functions

| Function         | Purpose                        |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Log Collection   | Gather logs from systems       |
| Monitoring       | Continuous security monitoring |
| Correlation      | Link related events            |
| Alerting         | Notify suspicious activity     |
| Visualization    | Dashboards & graphs            |
| Threat Detection | Detect attacks/anomalies       |

---

